        <div class="div-col"> 
            <h2>How to Test</h2>
            <p>There are a several different methods to test for bufferbloat. </p>
            <p>
                <strong>Note:</strong> for these tests it is highly recommended you are hardwired into your router.
                Wi-Fi introduces another layer of lag that may make the results inaccurate, which
                is outside of the scope of this site. Also, who games on Wi-Fi?
            </p>
            <br>
